Books about bookshops seem to have the exact same covers, look at the one from The Little Bookshop of Promises and The Library at the Edge of the World (by different authors no less). 
I also got more Dresden Files and books from The Lightbringer series (I’m trying to complete these series before I start reading them, as good a plan as any) and a few sci-fi/ fantasy books. None of these are on my TBR list for this year, except maybe the hermit one. 📚 
